title: DIAGNOSTIC PATHOLOGY: HOSPITAL AUTOPSY, 1E
description: Author: Billie Fyfe MD, Dylan V Miller MD Edition: 1 Har/Psc edition Publication Date: October 6, 2015 Publisher: Elsevier ISBN-10: 0323376762 ISBN-13: 978-0323376761 Pages: 424 pages Format: pdf Size: 92M --- Diagnostic Pathology: Hospital Autopsy, a volume in the highly regarded Diagnostic Pathology series, is the first reference to present autopsy pathology in the way in which it is practiced clinically. The unique approach in presenting classic autopsy techniques also emphasizes the role of molecular studies and other laboratory and ancillary tests (cytology, radiographic analysis) not commonly thought of during autopsy practice. --- http://dlfeb.com/book/diagnostic-pathology-hospital-autopsy-1e/
